Become a root user --> sudo su -

update the package --> apt update -y

Install the web-server apache2 -->

    2  apt install apache2 -y

To know all the running ports --> lsof -i -P -n | grep LISTEN

    4  cat /var/www/html/index.html
    5  cd /var/www/html/
    6  ls -l
    7  vi sre-course.html
